description: Numbers not in A036990 nor A036991.
links: Reinhard Zumkeller, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
formula: a(n) ~ n. [_Charles R Greathouse IV_, Sep 21 2011]
prog: (Haskell)a036992 n = a036992_list !! (n-1)a036992_list = c a036990_list (tail a036991_list) [0..] where   c us'@(u:us) vs'@(v:vs) (w:ws)     | w == u    = c us vs' ws     | w == v    = c us' vs ws     | otherwise = w : c us' vs' ws-- _Reinhard Zumkeller_, Jul 31 2013
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
